":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"想問吓可以去邊間買？"},{"pid":"ec7f867f8c2752d01772766690a7fbfcbff2603f","tid":2122391,"uid":117232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47f00123f81407c382e934e7038815553860c602","tid":2122391,"uid":185750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"想問吓可以去邊間買？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:17:28.000Z","msg":"你係長期需要consult 定要藥先？<br />\n<br />\nConsult 一定要醫保有包情緒病先病<br />\n無記錯FWD有呢類，但自己睇清楚包邊種情緒病。<br />\n同埋你申報完病歷，有機會exclude 你個病。<br />\n保險公司唔會明知蝕錢都幫你保。<br />\n<br />\n要藥的話，我見過呢d 例子，但唔鼓勵你做。<br />\n試下去家庭醫生，病徵寫頭痛果類"},{"pid":"88d984909df0b4b7705f8ada88ebd184c4ad53b1","tid":2122391,"uid":185750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:26:23.000Z","msg":"係長期政府醫院開藥個隻"},{"pid":"522c0040789c7ecb5a25274563b5c4acc10de713","tid":2122391,"uid":117232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88d984909df0b4b7705f8ada88ebd184c4ad53b1","tid":2122391,"uid":185750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:26:23.000Z","msg":"係長期政府醫院開藥個隻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:36:41.000Z","msg":"政府醫院開藥應該唔貴？<br />\n你買有包情緒病的醫保，保費唔會平，未必cover到你個cost"},{"pid":"6f36c35b2c400b8d679b637614669c00d2087fe7","tid":2122391,"uid":185750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:46:24.000Z","msg":"係想買一份傳統醫療保(包入院、大病)個d"},{"pid":"9ff8502fb3aba696dbdfff1c4ad7f369cc4280e8","tid":2122391,"uid":117232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f36c35b2c400b8d679b637614669c00d2087fe7","tid":2122391,"uid":185750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:46:24.000Z","msg":"係想買一份傳統醫療保(包入院、大病)個d"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:39:03.000Z","msg":"如果唔洗cover mental health 的醫保<br />\n建議搵Bupa 呢類只賣傳統醫保的公司。<br />\n好多時agent 會無啦啦係你份單度，加埋意外，危疾、殘疾呢d 附加保，令你保費好貴。"},{"pid":"d7533f714064a9d3f966e1d450869256dc346602","tid":2122391,"uid":111166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af89740fdf33a9853862c748441852a75d086ddb","tid":2122391,"uid":185750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7533f714064a9d3f966e1d450869256dc346602","tid":2122391,"uid":111166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f36c35b2c400b8d679b637614669c00d2087fe7","tid":2122391,"uid":185750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:46:24.000Z","msg":"係想買一份傳統醫療保(包入院、大病)個d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:43:37.000Z","msg":"tg?"},{"pid":"351cd7fabe62eb6aef775496fd373874c3ae063e","tid":2122391,"uid":111166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:43:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39be6074600c4785cba61d9a01072bf84b31d381","tid":2122391,"uid":360120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T10:14:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86319bcbd9e2a4d8c3c82a6df0b3b13ab5c8409f","tid":2122391,"uid":359652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T20:38:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f37ded2a0142d9b7f8d8e834be56f34a1b364604","tid":2122391,"uid":294072,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T03:13:18.000Z","msg":"你好啊，有情緒困擾真係唔容易啊。好多時候我地講出嚟都係想人明白，想人了解，但係成日比人話諗唔通。其實精神病都只不過係一種病，只不過係個腦有感冒。<br />\n<br />\n如果我話你知，有個平台你可以搵到同路人，你會唔會試下用啊？我想同你介紹一個為精神病患者而設嘅對話平台，Mentalok。喺呢個平台上面，只要你輸入關鍵詞，系統就會幫你配對另外一位輸入同一樣關鍵詞嘅用戶。當系統成功配對後，你地就可以開始傾計。<br />\n<br />\nMentalok呢個系統同其他平台有咩唔同？<br />\n第一，無人知道你係邊個。當你開網頁嘅時候，系統會隨機分派一個用戶編號比你，你唔需要輸入任何個人資料。<br />\n第二，你想幾時，邊到傾都得，完全無時間地域限制。<br />\n第三，亦都係最重要嘅，你唔單止係比人幫果一個，同時間你都係幫緊人果個。<br />\n<br />\n如果你有需要可以上呢個平台同人傾下計，或者你可以分享比身邊有需要嘅人！平台啱啱開無耐，可能會難啲配對到住。所以你嘅支持好重要！當然我唔希望你係有病果個，但係你都可以like and share 呢個post架！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mentalok.io/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalok.io%2F%20&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6H6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=f87a8967\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mentalok.io/ </a><br />\n<img src=\"https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/5f02875f97a15491f65dad87/5f159f1722d46d32dc1609a6_SEO%20Image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuploads-ssl.webflow.com%2F5f02875f97a15491f65dad87%2F5f159f1722d46d32dc1609a6_SEO%2520Image.jpg&h=78594fd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20c8f4d49320c4eea138f5239175e80a641750ac","tid":2122391,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:19:44.000Z","msg":"係另一個post一轉貼完實單出黎就好多保險狗出黎護航, 呢下呢個post又有冇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>呢個blog貼左簽名張單同埋今日非保證變成幾多<br />\n好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算死撚咗都小左30幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩個仔冇得讀大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hksufm.blogspot.com/2020/06/blog-post.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhksufm.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F06%2Fblog-post.html&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6H6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=fcbcb572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hksufm.blogspot.com/2020/06/blog-post.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-u4pPgmgHCEM/Xu9kdw2QGTI/AAAAAAAACBY/syuzdqA14GQmZfQCsVu1yPFVhSudW_wYQCK4BGAsYHg/s2880/螢幕截圖+2020-06-21+下午9.41.40.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-u4pPgmgHCEM%2FXu9kdw2QGTI%2FAAAAAAAACBY%2FsyuzdqA14GQmZfQCsVu1yPFVhSudW_wYQCK4BGAsYHg%2Fs2880%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%2B2020-06-21%2B%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%889.41.40.png&h=2960e4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-JWdk7f47Pbg/Xqa5BF5sCfI/AAAAAAAAB-w/PC-lxWqSfC8ToR4alHUsSSjzXcp8Z6Q9gCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/螢幕截圖+2020-04-27+下午6.50.26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-JWdk7f47Pbg%2FXqa5BF5sCfI%2FAAAAAAAAB-w%2FPC-lxWqSfC8ToR4alHUsSSjzXcp8Z6Q9gCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%2B2020-04-27%2B%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%886.50.26.png&h=c95195df&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d552b412ce87dde19b503e33fff3699f9405e651","tid":2122391,"uid":137123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T20:23:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7b3ffe71030df627039a2ba28b3a95db26975f4","tid":2122391,"uid":28815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ff8502fb3aba696dbdfff1c4ad7f369cc4280e8","tid":2122391,"uid":117232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f36c35b2c400b8d679b637614669c00d2087fe7","tid":2122391,"uid":185750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:46:24.000Z","msg":"係想買一份傳統醫療保(包入院、大病)個d"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:39:03.000Z","msg":"如果唔洗cover mental health 的醫保<br />\n建議搵Bupa 呢類只賣傳統醫保的公司。<br />\n好多時agent 會無啦啦係你份單度，加埋意外，危疾、殘疾呢d 附加保，令你保費好貴。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:36:02.000Z","msg":"你咪搞死人啦 人地已經有情緒病 病左仲要自己填claim form 你係咪搞笑？"},{"pid":"f0d07bdfc06d2d98f51e95bcf0e3661a3b0a8c72","tid":2122391,"uid":73515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17cbda8f72507e5f90eb049cb5352175c68cb9c7","tid":2122391,"uid":3013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"建議你搵返有d agent 公司搞，加你保費/除外條款係最好狀況。準備好哂d 醫院報告，如果唔齊料或者病情好反覆, 要有心理準備會被拒保。<br />\n<br />\n如果有frd 做，就搵佢地啦。 因為搞呢d 單underwrite 都麻煩，你比街一個陌生agent，唔係識你，其實好難有心機同你跟。"},{"pid":"fd8242213a01cd5178835517b814ae7844df6fbc","tid":2122391,"uid":3013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:44:44.000Z","msg":"你呢d case熟/有經驗嘅經紀真係好緊要，因為係counter offer 你過程一定會來來回回，你個agent 要幫你據理力爭"}]}